<node id="Retinopathy">
  <data key="d0">Retinopathy</data>
  <data key="d1">condition</data>
  <data key="d2">Retinopathy is a diabetes-related complication that affects the eyes and can lead to vision loss if not managed properly.&lt;SEP&gt;Retinopathy is a sight-threatening eye condition often asymptomatic, leading to lack of awareness among patients regarding its risks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e1400e1158e4f7be2283a0366ebf4f2</data>
