<node id="Diabetes Mellitus">
  <data key="d0">Diabetes Mellitus</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetes Mellitus is a chronic noncommunicable disease characterized by high blood sugar levels, significantly affecting a large segment of the global population. This condition, which can lead to serious health complications, is classified as a group of metabolic disorders that disrupt how the body processes glucose. Chronic hyperglycaemia results from defects in insulin secretion, action, or a combination of both, culminating in various health risks such as retinopathy, nephropathy, hypoglycaemia, and ketoacidosis.

Diabetes Mellitus manifests mainly in two forms: Type 1, where the body fails to produce insulin, and Type 2, which involves insulin resistance coupled with insufficient insulin production. It is essential that individuals managing Diabetes Mellitus adhere to specific management guidelines to mitigate risks associated with the disorder. Careful monitoring of blood sugar levels is critical, along with various diagnostic methods to ensure proper management of the condition.

The prevalence of Diabetes Mellitus is notably significant in regions such as the Eastern Mediterranean. Given its chronic nature, the condition necessitates ongoing treatment and poses substantial treatment costs. Overall, effective management and awareness of Diabetes Mellitus are vital to improving health outcomes for those affected by this widespread disorder.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-76910bb9e0e5a60b043dd2786bf63e97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25fb88c8ed14936954356d104de095d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b253411e54c35aa95f5f9179723bba3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12fe828372a20b6606e010f0fd5e6263&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e1400e1158e4f7be2283a0366ebf4f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e236a5eba0e1dbf843d32e509da045&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5384df975133ef2a52113cd3ca0f897e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85ef35aaa38ac4f0c032c8bc3f6df559&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f15f59b3ff05825a61f252ed8f9a74e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56d9ff3515afac60e7566e41837249a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92fbe09a650e62b7b6ea5d8769440e51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a560aca3f99b145384c2b736c2ceea1c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5fc5e661d0f94cc23c0188b9bbe4e08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8c827cc2249067692290d6a8a0e8018&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed87909b4bdb657354ca0eab1450156f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0748670b42b0f4e0b2ed9c5ce62d54e7</data>
