<node id="Photocoagulation">
  <data key="d0">Photocoagulation</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Photocoagulation is a laser treatment used to manage retinal diseases, particularly diabetic retinopathy, by creating small burns to seal leaking blood vessels.&lt;SEP&gt;Photocoagulation is a treatment method used to treat retinopathy by using laser technology to correct changes in the retina.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e1400e1158e4f7be2283a0366ebf4f2</data>
