  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Chronic complications of diabetes refer to long-term health issues that arise due to poorly managed diabetes, which can include eye, kidney, and nerve damage.&lt;SEP&gt;Chronic complications of diabetes refer to long-term health issues associated with diabetes mellitus, including diabetic neuropathy.</data>
