  <data key="d2">Taiwan is referenced in a study concerning the increasing prevalence of type 2 diabetes among children and adolescents.&lt;SEP&gt;Taiwan is referenced in a recent study showing type 2 diabetes as the leading cause of diabetes in children aged 6–18.</data>
