  <data key="d0">Metabolic Syndrome</data>
  <data key="d1">condition</data>
  <data key="d2">Metabolic syndrome is a cluster of conditions that increase the risk of heart disease and diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;Metabolic syndrome is a cluster of conditions, including hyperglycaemia, that increase the risk of heart disease, stroke, and diabetes.</data>
