  <data key="d0">Screening for Diabetes Mellitus</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Screening for diabetes mellitus involves testing individuals to identify diabetes in asymptomatic or minimally symptomatic individuals.&lt;SEP&gt;Screening for diabetes mellitus involves testing individuals to identify those at risk or diagnosed with diabetes, especially asymptomatic adults.</data>
