  <data key="d0">Glycaemic Control</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Glycaemic control is the management of blood sugar levels to prevent complications associated with diabetes, including retinopathy and nephropathy.&lt;SEP&gt;Glycaemic control refers to managing blood glucose levels to prevent complications of diabetes, including neuropathy.&lt;SEP&gt;Glycaemic control refers to the management of blood glucose levels in individuals with diabetes.</data>
