  <data key="d2">IGT refers to Impaired Glucose Tolerance, a condition indicating a higher risk for developing diabetes and cardiovascular disease.&lt;SEP&gt;Impaired Glucose Tolerance (IGT) is a prediabetic state of hyperglycemia that is associated with insulin resistance.</data>
