<node id="Diabetic Neuropathy">
  <data key="d0">Diabetic Neuropathy</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetic neuropathy is a microsvascular complication of diabetes mellitus, significantly affecting nerve structure due to hyperglycaemia.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetic neuropathy is a nerve disorder resulting from diabetes that can manifest in both peripheral and autonomic nervous systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0748670b42b0f4e0b2ed9c5ce62d54e7</data>
