<node id="Educational Programmes">
  <data key="d0">Educational Programmes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Educational programmes are designed to improve knowledge about diabetic neuropathy among primary care physicians and patients.&lt;SEP&gt;Educational programmes are initiatives aimed at informing patients and healthcare providers about the management of diabetic kidney disease and associated risks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0748670b42b0f4e0b2ed9c5ce62d54e7</data>
