  <data key="d0">Loop Diuretics</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Loop diuretics are a class of medications used to manage fluid retention in patients with kidney disease, often preferred over thiazide diuretics.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177</data>
