  <data key="d0">Thiazide Diuretics</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Thiazide diuretics are a class of medications used as initial therapy options for managing hypertension in diabetes patients.&lt;SEP&gt;Thiazide diuretics are a class of medications used to treat high blood pressure but may not be ideal for patients with fluid retention due to kidney disease.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-453e4228f98ddea76e07ce405d13fd32</data>
