<node id="Trans-Fatty Acids">
  <data key="d0">Trans-Fatty Acids</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Trans-fatty acids are a type of fat that raises LDL cholesterol and lowers HDL cholesterol, warranting their minimization in diet.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb0252816f7fbee4c50f79ef3ee56063</data>
