  <data key="d0">Distal Symmetrical Sensory-Motor Polyneuropathy</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Distal symmetrical sensory-motor polyneuropathy is the most common form of neuropathy, characterized by three stages: early, symptomatic, and severe.</data>
