  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Eastern Mediterranean countries are advised to prioritize the development of community-based healthy lifestyle programs to combat diabetes and its complications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa</data>
