<node id="Diabetes Control and Complications Trial">
  <data key="d0">Diabetes Control and Complications Trial</data>
  <data key="d1">study</data>
  <data key="d2">The Diabetes Control and Complications Trial is a study that highlighted the increased risks associated with intensive insulin therapy in diabetes patients.&lt;SEP&gt;The Diabetes Control and Complications Trial was a study in the USA that established the importance of glucose control in preventing complications in individuals with type 1 diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;The Diabetes Control and Complications Trial is a landmark study that examined the effects of tight blood glucose control on complications in insulin-dependent diabetes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942e000d0de99e8628ab9c8bcbe83419&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed87909b4bdb657354ca0eab1450156f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
